Azhani is a [[language]] spoken in [[Zarash'ak]] and the surrounding villages in the [[Shadow Marches]]. It descended from [[Vvaraa'shul]] and [[Goblin]], and has many linguistic traditions from the pre-[[Sundering]] [[Sarlona]]n kingdom of [[Corvagura]].